#prompt-linter ignore
    Rule: Emphasis Overuse
    Checks for excessive use of emphasis markers (**, !!, CAPS) that might diminish their impact.
    Ensures emphasis is used effectively and meaningfully.
#endignore

Check for overuse of emphasis markers (max 2-3 per prompt):
- Words like "important", "critical", "crucial", "essential"
- ALL CAPS text
- Multiple exclamation marks
- Repeated emphasis of the same point 